<div class="text parbase section">

    
    
    	<h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>

    


</div>
<div class="accordion-section section">
     
    <div class="container" data-analytics-region="Accordion">
        <div class="panel-group accordion standard" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">
              
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading1Standard1-col-parsys--8127369522072890414">
                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                            <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse1Standard1-col-parsys--8127369522072890414" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse1Standard1-col-parsys--8127369522072890414"> <span class="icon-down-chevron"></span> <span class="heading-text">
                                What is BT TV?
                                </span>
                            </a>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse1Standard1-col-parsys--8127369522072890414" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading1Standard1-col-parsys--8127369522072890414">
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <div>
                                <div class="text parbase section">

    
    
    	<p>BT TV is BT's best service ever, bringing you big entertainment for tiny prices.</p>
<p>We have a variety of clever little set-top boxes. With our Max 4K combo TV package you could step into the world of Ultra High definition with the 4k recordable TV box, which also gives you access to 1TB of memory. You can record up to 600 hours of SD TV, 250 hours of HD TV and 60 hours of Ultra HD TV.</p>
<p>If you choose Essential, Classic, Entertainment or Max 4K, you'll get a recordable TV box that lets you pause live TV, record up to 300 hours of standard definition programmes and access seven days of catch up TV.</p>
<p>If you choose Starter, you'll get a TV box that doesn't record but still lets you pause and rewind live TV.</p>
<p>All packages include BT Sport and up to 80 Freeview TV and radio channels, including up to 15 HD channels such as BBC One HD, Channel 4 HD and ITV HD.</p>
<p>You can add flexible TV bolt-ons to get the best in films, box sets, sports, kids' TV and music â all on convenient one-month contracts.</p>
<p>If you have standard BT Broadband you can add Starter or Essential. If you have Superfast Fibre you can add Starter, Classic or Entertainment which gives you 20 premium channelsâ , including BT Sport, Discovery Channel, MTV, Comedy Central, Gold, History and National Geographic.</p>
<p>Max 4K and Max 4K Sport 4K are available to those with Superfast Fibre line speed over 44mb and includes HD Extra, BT Sport in Ultra HD (Max 4K Sport 4K only) and BT TV App Extra.</p>

    


</div>


                            </div>
                            
                                  
                                    
                                
                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
