<ul style="list-style-position: inside;">
<li>A good quality outdoor TV aerial</li>
<li>A strong digital TV signal</li>
<li>A BT Home Hub and the right broadband speed for the TV service you choose. Use our broadband speed checker to see what line speeds you can get. If your line speed isn't fast enough, you may be able to boost it with our Broadband Accelerator</li>
