<div class="content-module">
<article class="article-page" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">
<div class="print-logo">
<img src="//img01.bt.co.uk/s/assets/040319/home/images/bt.png" alt="BT" />
</div>
<meta itemscope itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" itemType="https://schema.org/WebPage" itemid="http://home.bt.com/tech-gadgets/internet/broadband/what-is-complete-wifi-bt-broadband-bt-plus-11364313633457"/>
<meta itemprop="articleSection" content="broadband"/>
<div class="header-section">
<div class="subheader">
<h1 itemprop="headline">
Discover how to get strong wi-fi signal in every room of your home - guaranteed
</h1>
</div>
<div class="teaser-text-section">
<p itemprop="description">
Our new Complete Wi-Fi will help you get wall-to-wall wi-fi coverage and faster speeds in every corner of your home, so getting â and staying - online has never been easier.
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="details-section clearfix">
<div class="details-left" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
<meta itemprop="name" content="BT.com"/>
<a href="//home.bt.com/author/hannah-bouckley-31363802324361" rel="author">
<img src="/images/hannah-bouckley-136380232436106901-180423121707.png" class="thumbs-img" alt=Hannah Bouckley title="Hannah Bouckley" width="26" height="31">
</a>
<div class="details-left-text">
<div>
<span>By</span>
<span class="author-name">
<a href="//home.bt.com/author/hannah-bouckley-31363802324361" rel="author">Hannah Bouckley</a>
</span>&nbsp;
</div>
<div>
<span>Last updated:&nbsp;18 February 2019 - 5.39pm</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="details-right col-lg-4">
</div>
</div>
<div class="hero-image-section" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
<picture>
<source srcset='/images/complete-wi-fi-discover-how-we-guarantee-a-strong-wi-fi-signal-in-every-room-of-your-home-136431363317902601-181127102450.jpg' media="(min-width: 1200px)" class="img-responsive">
<source srcset='/images/complete-wi-fi-discover-how-we-guarantee-a-strong-wi-fi-signal-in-every-room-of-your-home-136431363317940701-181127102450.jpg' media="(min-width: 500px)" class="img-responsive">
<source srcset='/images/complete-wi-fi-discover-how-we-guarantee-a-strong-wi-fi-signal-in-every-room-of-your-home-136431363317910401-181127102450.jpg' media="(max-width: 499px)" class="img-responsive">
<img class="img-responsive" src=/images/complete-wi-fi-discover-how-we-guarantee-a-strong-wi-fi-signal-in-every-room-of-your-home-136431363317902601-181127102450.jpg srcset="/images/complete-wi-fi-discover-how-we-guarantee-a-strong-wi-fi-signal-in-every-room-of-your-home-136431363317902601-181127102450.jpg 1024w, /images/complete-wi-fi-discover-how-we-guarantee-a-strong-wi-fi-signal-in-every-room-of-your-home-136431363317940701-181127102450.jpg 500w, /images/complete-wi-fi-discover-how-we-guarantee-a-strong-wi-fi-signal-in-every-room-of-your-home-136431363317910401-181127102450.jpg 320w">
</picture>
<meta itemprop="url" content="http://home.bt.com">
<meta itemprop="height" content="365">
<meta itemprop="width" content="648">

</div>
<div class="article-body-section" itemprop="articleBody">
<p>
From a video calling to watching Netflix in bed, while your kids play game online, so many things we do today involve being connected to the internet.</p>
<p>
If your wi-fi signal is slow or you have blackspots around the home, it can be frustrating. With Complete Wi-Fi only we guarantee a strong wi-fi signal in every room of your home, so you can say goodbye to wi-fi issues and do what you want online, where you want.*</p>
<h3>
How does Complete Wi-Fi work?</h3>
<p>
Available to new Superfast and Ultrafast Fibre customers and existing BT Plus customers, Complete Wi-Fi delivers wall-to-wall coverage around your home, using Wi-Fi Discs to extend your hub&rsquo;s signal. So getting online from every corner of your home has never been easier.</p>
<p>
You can buy wi-fi extenders on the high street, but Complete Wi-Fi is different because it creates a single, seamless smart network. As you move around the house it will automatically connect to the hub or disc with the strongest signal, so you can enjoy a stable connection wherever you go, so whatever you are doing you won&rsquo;t get interrupted.</p>
<h3>
Do I need Complete Wi-Fi?</h3>
<p>
If you live in a larger house you may notice wi-fi blackspots in the rooms furthest away from your hub. Performance may slow down if more than one person is online at the same time.</p>
<p>
If you can&rsquo;t get a strong wi-fi signal, TV shows may freeze, video calls may judder and you might struggle to load the websites.</p>
<p>
Complete Wi-Fi can help by providing a strong wi-fi signal in each room in your home.</p>
<p>
Complete Wi-Fi has been trialled by our customers throughout the UK and has made a real difference. One triallist said: &ldquo;Our house is a barn conversion with 3ft deep stone walls, so coverage has always been an issue - no more.&rdquo;</p>
<p>
Another said: &ldquo;I've managed to get wi-fi signal in the bedroom upstairs which was the furthest away from my hub - so the wi-fi disc has come in very handy.&rdquo;</p>
<p>
Complete Wi-Fi has been awarded a&nbsp;Which? Best Buy.** The review commended the products performance: &ldquo;It lives up to its claims of a strong, reliable speedy connection in every room of the home and rightly deserves our Best Buy recommendation.&rdquo;</p>
<!-- Start - BT Video Embed for Publishers -->
<style type="text/css">
.bts_videojs_iframe_container { position: relative; height: 0; padding-bottom: 56.25% !important; margin-bottom: 15px; }.bts_videojs_iframe_container iframe { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0px; }</style>
<div class="bts_videojs_iframe_container">
<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" mozallowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" src="//players.brightcove.net/2045965034001/f07bffda-cbd1-4b3d-925e-6ed4baebf150_default/index.html?videoId=5972044291001" webkitallowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>
<!-- End -->
<h3>
<strong><span id="cke_bm_99S" style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span>What are the benefits of Complete Wi-Fi?<span id="cke_bm_99E" style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>
<p>
With Complete Wi-Fi you&rsquo;ll get faster wi-fi speeds so you should be able to stream HD content anywhere in your home.</p>
<p>
You&rsquo;ll also enjoy faster speeds in every room in your house, with a four-bedroom house potentially seeing an increase in speeds of up to 25% around the home with just one disc.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
With Complete Wi-Fi there&rsquo;s enough speed in each room for your whole family to go online. &ldquo;It can handle over eight devices streaming at the same time. Brilliant!&rdquo; said one of our Complete Wi-Fi triallists. Another said: &ldquo;It&rsquo;s been refreshingly stable &ndash; and no problems to explain to the kids.&rdquo;</p>
<p>
Our My BT app includes a Wi-Fi Manager which gives you control of your home wi-fi network. It will help you find the optimal location for your disc so you get the strongest signal everywhere and you can also use it to check the signal strength and find any weak spots.</p>
<p>
You can also use the app to see if other devices such as tablets, phones or laptops are connected. Even idle devices can impact on the performance of your wi-fi so the app can identify devices that can be disconnected or switched off.</p>
<p>
One disc is enough for most homes to get wall-to-wall wi-fi coverage, but in the unlikely event you don&rsquo;t get a strong signal in every room, we&rsquo;ll send you up to two more discs free of charge.</p>
<h3>
How do I get Complete Wi-Fi?</h3>
<p>
Complete Wi-Fi is available for new Superfast and Ultrafast Fibre customers for &pound;10 a month. If you&rsquo;ve got BT Plus, you can get Complete Wi-Fi now for just &pound;5 a month, just sign up via My BT.</p>
<p>
Sign up and we&rsquo;ll send you our new generation Smart Hub and one Wi-Fi Disc.</p>
<p>
<a href="https://www.productsandservices.bt.com/broadband/complete-wifi?s_intcid=con_intban_dmedia_Content_Tech_Storefront_completew_explainer" target="_blank"><strong>Already a BT Customer? Find out more about Complete Wi-Fi</strong></a></p>
<p>
<a href="https://www.bt.com/broadband/fibre/?s_intcid=con_intban_dmedia_Content_Tech_Storefront_completew_explainer" target="_blank"><strong>Not with us? Join us for Superfast Broadand</strong></a></p>
<h6>
<em>Complete Wi-Fi guarantee: we&rsquo;ll send you up-to two more discs to ensure a strong signal in every room of your home. If you still can&rsquo;t get a strong signal we&rsquo;ll give you a one-off credit of &pound;20 off your next BT bill. *Complete Wi-Fi with BT Plus 80% UK availability. Available to new and existing BT Plus customers. Existing customers will need to re-contract their BT Plus for 18 months. 18 month term. Price from month 19 currently &pound;63.99 a month for BT Plus with Complete Wi-Fi. If you cancel Complete Wi-Fi you&rsquo;ll need to return the Wi-Fi discs, or else you&rsquo;ll be charged &pound;30 per disc. When you take Complete Wi-Fi, you&rsquo;ll be sent a Smart Hub2, if you cancel BT Plus within 12 months you&rsquo;ll be charged up to &pound;45 towards the cost of your Smart Hub2. BT Plus is linked to the broadband product you&rsquo;re on &ndash; if you cancel or move to a broadband product that is not part of Plus, you will lose your benefits. Includes Unlimited Weekend Calls, BT Virus Protect, 1000GB Cloud and a BT Smart Hub 2. Payment by Direct Debit. Subject to availability, minimum line speed and computer specification.&nbsp;BT Plus with Complete Wi-Fi 80% UK availability. Available to new and existing BT Plus customers who sign up for 18 months. Price from month 19 currently &pound;63.99. If you cancel Complete Wi-Fi you&rsquo;ll need to return the Wi-Fi discs, or you&rsquo;ll be charged &pound;30 per disc. You&rsquo;ll also need to pay up-to &pound;45 towards the cost of your Smart Hub2 if you cancel in the first 12 months. BT Plus is linked to the broadband product you&rsquo;re on &ndash; if you cancel or move to a broadband product that is not part of Plus, you will lose your benefits. Includes Unlimited Weekend Calls, BT Virus Protect, 1000GB Cloud and a BT Smart Hub 2. Payment by Direct Debit. Subject to availability, minimum line speed and computer specification. Terms apply, see bt.com/BTPlusterms. Broadband Backup, Mobile Data Boost and Fastest 4G Speed apply to BT Mobile plans on the same billing account as your Plus Broadband. **<a href="https://www.which.co.uk/reviews/wifi-routers-and-extenders/bt-complete-wifi/review?utm_campaign=bestbuyicon&amp;utm_medium=endorsement&amp;utm_source=BT" target="_blank">Which</a></em></h6>
</div>
