                            <div>
                                <div class="text parbase section">

    
    
    	<p>You can watch BT Sport in stunning high definition on the Sky Digital Satellite Platform, or on BT TV with BT Superfast Fibre Broadband.</p>
<p>Select your package and then choose HD before you checkout.</p>
<p><a href="/sport/tv/"><span class="bold">See BT TV packages with BT Sport</span></a></p>
<p><a href="/sport/sky/"><span class="bold">See how to watch BT Sport on Sky</span></a></p>
<p>If you've got a HD subscription with Sky, this won't work with BT Sport. You'll need to add BT Sport HD to your BT Sport package.</p>
<p>To watch in HD, you'll need a HD-ready TV that's connected to your set-top box using a HDMI cable. If you're watching on the Sky Digital Satellite Platform, you'll also need a black Sky box.<br />
</p>

    


</div>


