                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <div>
                                <div class="text parbase section">

    
    
    	<p>We have two types of broadband: BT Superfast Fibre and standard BT Broadband.</p>
<p>BT Superfast Fibre gives you a superfast fibre optic broadband connection with average speeds of 67Mb. This lets you do more online, with everyone online together, and it's great for downloading or streaming movies, TV shows and music. You can watch iPlayer with less interruption and HD video with less buffering.</p>
<p>If you can't get BT Superfast Fibre or if you live in a home with lighter internet usage and fewer devices, standard BT Broadband is ideal for you. It's perfect for everyday browsing, uploading and sharing photos and updates on your favourite sites and streaming content online.</p>

    


