                            <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse5Standard1-col-parsys--2451066616078843878" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5Standard1-col-parsys--2451066616078843878"> <span class="icon-down-chevron"></span> <span class="heading-text">
                                How do I get BT Sport in HD?
                                </span>
                            </a>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse5Standard1-col-parsys--2451066616078843878" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading5Standard1-col-parsys--2451066616078843878">
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <div>
                                <div class="text parbase section">

    
    
    	<p>You can watch BT Sport in stunning high definition on the Sky Digital Satellite Platform, or on BT TV with BT Superfast Fibre Broadband.</p>
<p>Select your package and then choose HD before you checkout.</p>
<p><a href="/sport/tv/"><span class="bold">See BT TV packages with BT Sport</span></a></p>
<p><a href="/sport/sky/"><span class="bold">See how to watch BT Sport on Sky</span></a></p>
<p>If you've got a HD subscription with Sky, this won't work with BT Sport. You'll need to add BT Sport HD to your BT Sport package.</p>
<p>To watch in HD, you'll need a HD-ready TV that's connected to your set-top box using a HDMI cable. If you're watching on the Sky Digital Satellite Platform, you'll also need a black Sky box.<br />
</p>

    


</div>


                            </div>
                            
                                  
                                    
                                
                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
              
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading6Standard1-col-parsys--2451066616078843878">
                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                            <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse6Standard1-col-parsys--2451066616078843878" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse6Standard1-col-parsys--2451066616078843878"> <span class="icon-down-chevron"></span> <span class="heading-text">
                                Can I get BT Sport in more than one room?
