                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse6Standard1-col-parsys--2451066616078843878" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading6Standard1-col-parsys--2451066616078843878">
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <div>
                                <div class="text parbase section">

    
    
    	<p>If you're on the Sky Digital Satellite Platform, you can watch BT Sport at home on a second TV if you have BT Sport Second Box. You'll need a second Sky box and second viewing card to order.</p>
<p>If you've got BT Sport HD, you'll be able to watch it on both your boxes. You won't need an extra BT Sport HD subscription.</p>

    


</div>


