                        <div class="panel-body">
                            <div>
                                <div class="text parbase section">

    
    
    	<p>Sorry, but the BT Sport app and online player is only available on its own with BT Broadband packages, and is free for 3 months then costs Â£10 a month. The app and online player is also included for free if you order BT Sport on BT TV, Sky TV or TalkTalk TV.<br />
</p>

    


