                            <div>
                                <div class="text parbase section">

    
    
    	<p>The minimum download speed is the lowest speed we think you should get with this package.</p>
<p>You can test the speed to your hub in My BT. If itâs slower than it should be, get in touch and weâll do our best to fix it.</p>
<p>If we canât improve it within 30 days, you can leave your contract without penalty. This is because weâve signed up to the Ofcom Voluntary Codes of Practice on Broadband Speed.</p>
<p>If youâve got one of our Ultrafast packages, youâll also get a speed guarantee of at least 100Mb, and an upload speed guarantee of 10Mb. If you test the speed to your hub and itâs lower than it should be, you can claim Â£20. You can make a claim up to four times a year.</p>

    


