    	<p><b></b><span class="notes"><b>Calls to service numbers</b></span></p>
<p><span class="notes">Calls to service numbers starting 084, 087, 09 &amp; 118 consist of a 15p per minute access charge from BT, plus a service charge set by the company you call. Both charges are calculated excluding VAT, so when we round the price and add the VAT, some calls will round up by up to 2p, depending on the length of the call.Â You can find the full details in ourÂ <a href="https://www.bt.com/assets/pdf/BT_PhoneTariff_Residential.pdf">tariff guide</a>.<br />
</span></p>
<p><span class="notes"><b>International Freedom</b></span></p>
<p><span class="notes">Only Â£8.50 a month. Includes calls to landlines in 36 International destinations. For residential customers on a BT Calling Plan. Minimum 1 month term. Fair use policy (calls over 600 minutes a month will be charged at 6p a minute) and Terms and Conditions apply. Some regions are included or excluded within countries:</span></p>
<ul style="list-style-position: inside;">
<li><span class="notes">Australia includes the Christmas Islands &amp; Cocos Islands</span></li>
<li><span class="notes">Cyprus excludes Northern Cyprus</span></li>
<li><span class="notes">Ireland is the Republic of Ireland. The 0p a minute rate for calls to fixed lines in the Republic of Ireland does not apply to customers calling from Northern Ireland</span></li>
<li><span class="notes">Italy includes the Vatican City</span></li>
<li><span class="notes">New Zealand includes the Chatham Islands</span></li>
<li><span class="notes">Spain includes the Canary Islands</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span class="notes"><b>Friends &amp; Family International</b></span></p>
<p><span class="notes">Only Â£2 a month. A 23p call set up fee applies.</span></p>
<p><span class="notes"><b>BT SmartTalk</b></span></p>
<p><span class="notes">You'll need a BT home calling plan and an iPhone/Android Smartphone connected to Wi-Fi or 3G. Five users per account. SmartTalk allows you to access your calling plan on your smartphone. UK time zone applies. Opt-in for international, premium (09) and personal (070) calls. Fair-use policy applies. Excludes BT Basic. <a href="http://www2.bt.com/static/i/btretail/panretail/terms/index.html">SeeÂ details</a>. Each BT SmartTalk user must have their own unique BT.com log-in details. It's easy to set these up after you've downloaded the app. Just press the Create BT Login button.</span></p>
