<p><span class="notes">If a reward was offered on the date you placed your order, it will expire 3 months after the date your broadband order was installed or mobile order activated, unless you claim your reward. BT reserves the right to remove the offer at any time. Rewards are subject to suppliers own terms and conditions.</span></p>
