<p><span class="notes"><b>Extra SpeedÂ </b>- With Extra Speed 4G, the maximum speed available through the network is capped at 60 Mbps rather than 30 Mbps on our standard 4G. The speeds you get on your phone will be lower, and depend on things like the number of users, distance from the mast and the type of 4G phone you have. This add on is valid from the moment you buy it and then runs on a 30 day rolling contract. Extra Speed 4G is not available on BT Business Mobile plans.</span></p>
<p><span class="notes"><b>RoamingÂ </b>- Travel Data Pass is a daily data roaming add-on available to all new and existing BT Mobile customers. USA Data Roaming add-ons are no longer available for sale. They are valid for 30 days or until you've used up all the data â whichever comes first.</span></p>
<p><span class="notes"><b>Wi-Fi Calling</b></span></p>
<p><span class="notes">Available on selected enabled BT Mobile handset plans and iPhone 5S and above. Wi-Fi connection required. All calls or texts charged as per your BT Mobile plan. Terms apply.</span></p>
<p><span class="notes"><b>4G Calling</b></span></p>
<p><span class="notes">Available on selected enabled BT Mobile handset plans and iPhone 6 and above. 4G connection required. All calls or texts charged as per your BT Mobile plan. Terms apply.</span></p>
<p><span class="notes"><b>Wi-Fi / 4G Calling</b></span></p>
<p><span class="notes">Available on selected enabled BT Mobile handset plans. 4G Calling also available on iPhone 6 and above â 4G connection required. Wi-Fi Calling also available on iPhone 5S and above - Wi-Fi connection required. All calls or texts charged as per your BT Mobile plan. Terms apply.</span></p>
